reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Great durable quality, thick and sturdy
reviews.reviewText: I used these baskets to set at each end of my bar, they have many uses. They can hold plants, bottles of wine or liquor or to use in a bathroom for your rolled up hand towels and wash clothes.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on May 4, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 4.0 out of 5 stars Nice basket but...
reviews.reviewText: This would be a great basket for toys, yarn, and other gadgets, especially for kids and pups. It seems to be sturdy and washable. However, I needed this for a craft to make into a wedding gift, and here is where I had the problem. When it arrived, it is folded it up and put into plastic. I could never get it back to its originalshape of a basket. They will give you instructions on how to get it back to its original shape, but that does not work.
